# Emoticon Sprites

This directory contains emoticon sprites for the EmoticonView component.

## Emoticon Types

- heart.tres - Satisfaction (❤️)
- star.tres - Moved (⭐)
- yummy.tres - Tasty (😋)
- thinking.tres - Thinking (💭)
- question.tres - Curious (❓)

## Specifications

- Size: 16×16 pixels (displayed at 48×48)
- Format: AtlasTexture or ImageTexture resources
